description: Italy and Spain feel abandoned, as the crisis really brings into question what the EU is all about.
title: Coronavirus outbreak eats into EU unity
title_page: Coronavirus outbreak eats into EU unity - BBC News
maintext: But rich, europhile countries like Germany are not yet digging deeper in to their pockets to help out poorer Italy and Spain. There's little sense of the responsibility West Germany felt towards the East after the fall of the Berlin Wall.
